{"tid":1767854,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找最愛來感激今次分開","createTime":"2019-12-03T15:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T08:01:27.000Z","uid":210182,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"752011d29f9fed49280294bc86b789ee7e1cb2eb","tid":1767854,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"回頭都找不到曙光 別再看 別再望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人臨近聖誕會諗返上年點過<br />\n依家天氣一凍就諗返起之前既野真係想死<br />\n希望男朋友無追蹤到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係叫下春姐<br />\n唔知佢係咪仲好掛住ex 我好驚慢慢開始會抽離 <br />\n唔係一心一意邊有一齊既意思架 <br />\n仲話無刻意諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔係放低左只係唔諗起<br />\n我唔追求任何物質 或者要對方比到咩我<br />\n只需要一個全心全意會專一個心只有對方既人<br />\n但貌似呢個世代好難搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5f95f5ad8d06e6b0c83c6a541e4a5af92f6335","tid":1767854,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"po完又淆底明明係我好應該唔開心既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e1bd96a5029d2cc855d7be8d8495246b5f6b32","tid":1767854,"uid":175580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"經歷過幾個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉 好攰了&hellip;"},{"pid":"8f165360718a3edca176465dfb83e671f7bab7af","tid":1767854,"uid":141901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:45:27.000Z","msg":"無經驗答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請善用不推文回覆</span></div>"},{"pid":"cea960d1ac78d63e73983d0bf159c6b79ea38a86","tid":1767854,"uid":200587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 